---
// FAQ Component for Veritas GRC
---

<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="faq-container">
    
    <div class="faq-header">
      <span class="faq-subtitle">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</span>
      <h2 class="faq-title">Navigating Clinical Research Governance & Compliance</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <!-- Item 1 -->
      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary class="faq-question">
          What core compliance frameworks does Veritas GRC specialize in?
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We provide comprehensive advisory and structural oversight across major global and regional standards, including Good Clinical Practice (GCP), FDA regulations, EMA directives, and local Kenyan clinical trial regulatory frameworks.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Item 2 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          How do your governance solutions accelerate clinical development timelines?
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>By proactively aligning protocols with strict regulatory and data privacy requirements from day one, we eliminate costly compliance bottlenecks, minimize regulatory pushback, and prevent protocol deviations during trials.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Item 3 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          Do you provide data privacy framework support for health data?
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. We implement robust clinical trial data governance structures designed to satisfy the strict data collection, storage, and transfers mandates required by regional data protection laws and health regulations.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Item 4 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          What types of research entities do you partner with?
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We collaborate across the entire clinical development matrix, including institutional sponsors, multinational pharmaceutical developers, biotechnology innovators, and research investigator sites.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.faq-section {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 6rem auto;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
  font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
}

.faq-container {
  display: flex;
  gap: 3rem;
}

.faq-header {
  flex: 1 1 40%;
}

.faq-subtitle {
  color: #1a3e6f;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.faq-title {
  color: #0f172a;
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.25;
  margin: 0;
}

.faq-list {
  flex: 1 1 60%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.faq-item {
  background: #ffffff;
  border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
}

.faq-item[open] {
  border-color: #1a3e6f;
}

.faq-question {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1e293b;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  user-select: none;
}

.faq-question::-webkit-details-marker {
  display: none;
}

.faq-icon {
  position: relative;
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* Custom pure CSS arrows that shift down when active */
.faq-icon::before,
.faq-icon::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  background-color: #4a5568;
  transition: transform 0.2s ease;
}

.faq-icon::before {
  top: 7px;
  left: 0;
  width: 16px;
  height: 2px;
}

.faq-icon::after {
  top: 0;
  left: 7px;
  width: 2px;
  height: 16px;
}

.faq-item[open] .faq-icon::after {
  transform: rotate(90deg);
  opacity: 0;
}

.faq-item[open] .faq-icon::before {
  transform: rotate(180deg);
  background-color: #1a3e6f;
}

.faq-answer {
  padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  color: #4a5568;
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-size: 0.975rem;
}

.faq-answer p {
  margin: 0;
}

/* Responsive adjustment for clean viewports */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .faq-container {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .faq-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }
}
</style>
